Name
       timing_disable_internal_inout_cell_paths

Syntax
       timing_disable_internal_inout_cell_paths

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       When  set  to false, enables internal bidirectional feedback paths that
       are completely contained in one instance.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

